org.cloudsimplus.util.tablebuilder

Interface TableColumn

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTableColumn, CsvTableColumn, HtmlTableColumn, TextTableColumn

    public interface TableColumn
    An interface that represents a column of a table generated using a TableBuilder.
    Author:
    Manoel Campos da Silva Filho
